  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Change in various clinical symptoms of neurological disorders</measure>
    <time_frame>1 year</time_frame>
    <description>Change in various symptoms such as muscle strength, limb strength, ambulation, neck holding, bladder bowel management, spasticity, sensation, speech, etc depending on the disorder will be recorded at 1 year follow up. Percentage analysis of each symptom will be carried out to study the benefits of stem cell therapy on them.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
